{
  "texts": [
    "Furthermore, GPT-4 has been observed to perform poorly in pure calculation tasks [35], probably also challenging strictly numerical criteria.",
    "This is not entirely surprising, as GPT-4 is a LLM (with an emphasis on language) and is not intended to be used as a calculator.We found only 1 mistake that could be classified at the Bloom's taxonomy level labeled \"evaluate,\" in which GPT-4 incorrectly judged a medically complex situation.",
    "LimitationsThis study has some limitations that merit discussion.",
    "First, we used Bloom's taxonomy.",
    "While it provides good operationalization for cognitive processes, the taxonomy represents a continuum wherein more than 1 level can be activated in a single question [8]."
  ]
}